                </span></li>

                <li>&nbsp;银行贷款余额<span>
                    <input type="tel" name="BankLoanBalance" id="BankLoanBalance" value="" class="fxf gx" style="border: 0px" datatype="m" placeholder="银行贷款余额"></span> </li>


                <li>&nbsp;是否银行逾期<span>
